title: Lunchbox Gives Away TV Prize To Wrong Person + Dustin Lynch Talks About His Relationship Status

description:
Lunchbox accidentally gives away a TV to the wrong person. Dustin Lynch stops by and talks new music and about his dating life. Also, Bobby talks about getting emotional at the funeral he was asked to speak at.
